{"lang":"es","stage":6,"title":"longer everyday sentences","sentences":[{"t":"Fui a la fiesta.","en":"I went to the party.","a":"n_e21a7d1f296f.mp3"},{"t":"¿Vienes a la fiesta?","en":"Are you coming to the party?","a":"n_1be37b69c1cd.mp3"},{"t":"El bus llega ya.","en":"The bus is coming now.","a":"n_8d8a46a7fc2a.mp3"},{"t":"Vivo cerca de aquí.","en":"I live close to here.","a":"n_e865452406c4.mp3"},{"t":"Él conoce a todos.","en":"He knows everyone.","a":"n_121ba914defe.mp3"},{"t":"Me duele la cabeza.","en":"My head hurts.","a":"n_3db51bdd2fd9.mp3"},{"t":"Llega en cinco minutos.","en":"It arrives in five minutes.","a":"n_c343f593a464.mp3"},{"t":"Deberías decir la verdad.","en":"You should tell the truth.","a":"n_dd9a94004254.mp3"},{"t":"Deberías descansar un poco.","en":"You should rest a little.","a":"n_d5952ce3520d.mp3"},{"t":"Esto está muy rico.","en":"This is delicious.","a":"n_bf91553a5bd6.mp3"},{"t":"No puedo esperar más.","en":"I can't wait any longer.","a":"n_3a4e737ffbdf.mp3"},{"t":"Quiero ver qué pasa.","en":"I want to see what happens.","a":"n_81b25a9b5613.mp3"},{"t":"Vuelvo en una hora.","en":"I'll be back in an hour.","a":"n_c5db229640b5.mp3"},{"t":"Quiero algo para tomar.","en":"I want something to drink.","a":"n_bbc56f30ca66.mp3"},{"t":"¿Qué vas a tomar?","en":"What are you going to drink?","a":"n_6b87d6d8e76d.mp3"},{"t":"Voy a tomar agua.","en":"I'll have water.","a":"n_05802e1bcb85.mp3"},{"t":"Esta vez pago yo.","en":"This time I'm paying.","a":"n_819be0e6d008.mp3"},{"t":"Está a la derecha.","en":"It's on the right.","a":"n_59bf1af066b8.mp3"},{"t":"Gira a la derecha.","en":"Turn right.","a":"n_12598561cd81.mp3"},{"t":"Mejor ve en taxi.","en":"Better go by taxi.","a":"n_9d286fbff1bf.mp3"},{"t":"Ella es mi amiga.","en":"She's my friend.","a":"n_f8b3878b230f.mp3"},{"t":"¿Es ella tu amiga?","en":"Is she your friend?","a":"n_0dd8b53bb450.mp3"},{"t":"Esta es mi amiga.","en":"This is my friend.","a":"n_4c65f0c91993.mp3"},{"t":"Por fin es viernes.","en":"It's finally Friday.","a":"n_c4f61347d7e4.mp3"},{"t":"Estoy feliz de verte.","en":"I'm happy to see you.","a":"n_8af108c7ea6e.mp3"},{"t":"Vengo a verte después.","en":"I'm coming to see you later.","a":"n_7aeff969f0f0.mp3"},{"t":"Ella tiene un gato.","en":"She has a cat.","a":"n_9106a464dbaf.mp3"},{"t":"Prefiero quedarme en casa.","en":"I'd rather stay home.","a":"n_e30e4e1dcf57.mp3"},{"t":"Vamos a llegar tarde.","en":"We're going to be late.","a":"n_c5d410ca9469.mp3"},{"t":"¿Me haces un favor?","en":"Can you do me a favor?","a":"n_0dc40b039867.mp3"},{"t":"¿Qué es bueno aquí?","en":"What's good here?","a":"n_b74db09bef09.mp3"},{"t":"Mira el lado bueno.","en":"Look on the bright side.","a":"n_53242c6656a7.mp3"},{"t":"Dame una buena razón.","en":"Give me one good reason.","a":"n_9317e132ebc8.mp3"},{"t":"Esto es más fácil.","en":"This is easier.","a":"n_634b62109b82.mp3"},{"t":"Antes era más fácil.","en":"It used to be easier.","a":"n_aa360cda5564.mp3"},{"t":"Está a la izquierda.","en":"It's on the left.","a":"n_02bfc1f61164.mp3"},{"t":"Gira a la izquierda.","en":"Turn left.","a":"n_4fcf80e99ed6.mp3"},{"t":"Voy a la estación.","en":"I'm going to the station.","a":"n_431bb6f92c12.mp3"},{"t":"¿Dónde está la estación?","en":"Where is the station?","a":"n_864fa2403817.mp3"},{"t":"Comí algo rico ayer.","en":"I ate something tasty yesterday.","a":"n_93cae7a52e1e.mp3"},{"t":"Estoy listo para empezar.","en":"I'm ready to start.","a":"n_51a18ad2a6bd.mp3"},{"t":"Sé cocinar un poco.","en":"I know how to cook a little.","a":"n_e7d05251fd25.mp3"},{"t":"Nadie quiere comprar eso.","en":"Nobody wants to buy that.","a":"n_b13ffa83bbd2.mp3"},{"t":"Me debes cinco euros.","en":"You owe me five euros.","a":"n_f538177b3375.mp3"},{"t":"Conozco bien el camino.","en":"I know the way well.","a":"n_39458f5a6d4e.mp3"},{"t":"Esta noche no salgo.","en":"I'm not going out tonight.","a":"n_9fca91db6316.mp3"},{"t":"¿Puedo preguntar una cosa?","en":"Can I ask one thing?","a":"n_c515d0a5ab6c.mp3"},{"t":"¿Cómo te lo digo?","en":"How do I tell you this?","a":"n_e95bcd1ace48.mp3"},{"t":"¿Qué le digo ahora?","en":"What do I tell him now?","a":"n_0da39f2ab60b.mp3"},{"t":"Él sabe la respuesta.","en":"He knows the answer.","a":"n_5094a72be100.mp3"},{"t":"Le di las gracias.","en":"I thanked her.","a":"n_08f21b2c5b26.mp3"},{"t":"No estamos listos todavía.","en":"We're not ready yet.","a":"n_46844a305677.mp3"},{"t":"Necesito tiempo para pensar.","en":"I need time to think.","a":"n_c82c8e6e31fc.mp3"},{"t":"Mi casa es pequeña.","en":"My house is small.","a":"n_fa4f8283a58d.mp3"},{"t":"Tenemos una casa pequeña.","en":"We have a small house.","a":"n_c87409c511ff.mp3"},{"t":"Me gusta esta canción.","en":"I like this song.","a":"n_e656dfefdd36.mp3"},{"t":"Yo no dije nada.","en":"I didn't say anything.","a":"n_1a61e3ccd2eb.mp3"},{"t":"Ya sé cómo funciona.","en":"I already know how it works.","a":"n_213c6a36b54e.mp3"},{"t":"Ella se levanta temprano.","en":"She gets up early.","a":"n_7dcce139f559.mp3"},{"t":"¿Qué tienen para tomar?","en":"What do you have to drink?","a":"n_126313b6ef12.mp3"},{"t":"¿Me trae más pan?","en":"Can you bring me more bread?","a":"n_77166343dee6.mp3"},{"t":"Ella vive en casa.","en":"She lives at home.","a":"n_d7b067044bbe.mp3"},{"t":"Trabajo hasta las seis.","en":"I work until six.","a":"n_46ee897b6aa8.mp3"},{"t":"Quiero vender mi teléfono.","en":"I want to sell my phone.","a":"n_1e8e6591590d.mp3"},{"t":"¿Dónde compro el boleto?","en":"Where do I buy the ticket?","a":"n_0b2acfc3e709.mp3"},{"t":"Me duele la garganta.","en":"My throat hurts.","a":"n_91483acdda87.mp3"},{"t":"Es un amigo mío.","en":"He's a friend of mine.","a":"n_939c9eedc0a5.mp3"},{"t":"El gusto es mío.","en":"The pleasure is mine.","a":"n_ec354e41ba3a.mp3"},{"t":"Estoy muy ocupada hoy.","en":"I'm really busy today.","a":"n_a4d7722dd88d.mp3"},{"t":"Mis amigos están felices.","en":"My friends are happy.","a":"n_38e67ae848a5.mp3"},{"t":"Estoy triste de irme.","en":"I'm sad to leave.","a":"n_9d10c8b94468.mp3"},{"t":"Casi nunca llego temprano.","en":"I almost never arrive early.","a":"n_2076137f11bf.mp3"},{"t":"Necesitamos comer algo ya.","en":"We need to eat something now.","a":"n_fbe474b8ea1a.mp3"},{"t":"Me encanta el chocolate.","en":"I love chocolate.","a":"n_80b38c23cc34.mp3"},{"t":"Me gusta el sol.","en":"I like the sun.","a":"n_342bcd84ac69.mp3"},{"t":"¿Prefieres café o té?","en":"Do you prefer coffee or tea?","a":"n_721c6c84b863.mp3"},{"t":"Me gustaría verte pronto.","en":"I'd like to see you soon.","a":"n_605ab30890f5.mp3"},{"t":"No puedo decirte ahora.","en":"I can't tell you now.","a":"n_81f3a7586a6a.mp3"},{"t":"Llegué muy temprano hoy.","en":"I got here really early today.","a":"n_9020accc9470.mp3"},{"t":"Ella viene con nosotros.","en":"She's coming with us.","a":"n_62a5078f6a9c.mp3"},{"t":"Salimos en cinco minutos.","en":"We're leaving in five minutes.","a":"n_6dfc6df8722a.mp3"},{"t":"¿Ya hiciste la tarea?","en":"Did you do the homework yet?","a":"n_87d9a2cc11b9.mp3"},{"t":"¿Por qué preguntas tanto?","en":"Why do you ask so much?","a":"n_5224a3b76be3.mp3"},{"t":"Él hace muchas preguntas.","en":"He asks a lot of questions.","a":"n_b3c3dff52db7.mp3"},{"t":"No quiero contar nada.","en":"I don't want to tell anyone anything.","a":"n_e2a66b89cf4b.mp3"},{"t":"Nos vemos esta tarde.","en":"See you this afternoon.","a":"n_6bc301b11d36.mp3"},{"t":"No sé su nombre.","en":"I don't know his name.","a":"n_aa927a29db5f.mp3"},{"t":"Ella conoce mi historia.","en":"She knows my story.","a":"n_56759b4b166e.mp3"},{"t":"Me duele la mano.","en":"My hand hurts.","a":"n_e74725191664.mp3"},{"t":"Te doy mi número.","en":"I'll give you my number.","a":"n_8f24516c2686.mp3"},{"t":"Muéstrame cómo se hace.","en":"Show me how it's done.","a":"n_582515181778.mp3"},{"t":"Te di mi palabra.","en":"I gave you my word.","a":"n_15396cbb93c8.mp3"},{"t":"¿Me das un poco?","en":"Will you give me some?","a":"n_3bf4aaae4ee3.mp3"},{"t":"¿Viste cómo me miró?","en":"Did you see how he looked at me?","a":"n_f4022266e772.mp3"}]}